# fix a failing test until the CLI suite is green
loop "fix test":
  goal: the CLI test suite passes
  look at: src/, test/, and the last failure
  allow edits automatically
  each cycle: plan, then act, then observe
  done when "npm test" passes
  when it fails: reflect on the last failure, then plan again
  when it passes and the goal is met: stop
  after 6 tries: stop and warn "test still red after 6 tries — needs a human"
